=Description=

"Qoin designs, implements and supports Community Currencies. We help to set up and manage Community Currencies ‘out of the box’, as well as tailor made Complementary Currencies. We also research the impact of Community Currencies and develop new tools and approaches to increase this impact.  Qoin is a Dutch not-for-profit organisation founded in 1998."

